// Browse Dashboard
// Topic browser with category filter tabs and a grid of topic cards.
// Entry point for the onboarding browse mode.

FUNCTION BrowseDashboard()                                              EXPORT
  CALLS: getTopics (onboarding-api), getCategories (onboarding-api)
  Read project from OnboardingContext.
  On mount (or project change): fetch topics and categories in parallel.
  Maintain selectedCategory state (default: 'all').
  Compute filteredTopics: if a category is selected, restrict to topics in that category's topic list.
  Render:
    - Category filter tabs (All + one per category with counts).
    - A 3-column grid of topic cards, each linking to /onboarding/topic/:name.
